comment: Mills (SAS) cleanly strips the ball from Johnson (MIA).
Leonard (SAS) cleanly strips the ball from Whiteside (MIA) and any contact to his hand when it is part of the ball is considered incidental.
Gasol (SAS) sets the screen on Waiters (MIA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Leonard (SAS) makes marginal contact with Dragic (MIA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Leonard (SAS) draws Waiters (MIA) into the air towards him and the body contact occurs during his shooting motion.
Waiters (MIA) makes marginal contact with Ginobili (SAS) on the drive to the basket.
Johnson (MIA) commits a take foul on Leonard (SAS).
Winslow (MIA) reaches in for the steal on Leonard (SAS) and any contact is incidental.
Babbitt (MIA) commits a take foul on Leonard (SAS).
